# Copie este arquivo para .env.local e preencha com seus dados

## Database
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/lmg_platform?schema=public"

## NextAuth
NEXTAUTH_URL="http://localhost:3000"
NEXTAUTH_SECRET="your-super-secret-key-change-this-in-production-min-32-chars"

## App
NODE_ENV="development"
APP_URL="http://localhost:3000"

## Open Finance - Pluggy (opcional)
PLUGGY_CLIENT_ID="your-pluggy-client-id"
PLUGGY_CLIENT_SECRET="your-pluggy-client-secret"
PLUGGY_WEBHOOK_SECRET="your-pluggy-webhook-secret"

## Kiwify
KIWIFY_WEBHOOK_SECRET="your-kiwify-webhook-secret"

## Email transacional
RESEND_API_KEY="re_your_resend_api_key"
EMAIL_FROM="Equipe Plataforma <acesso@seudominio.com>"
